reviewText: Awful!! Anti- santisima muerte propaganda! They propose that la Santa muerte is in league with the devil and to worship her is to turn away from Jesus! What garbage, most devotees of Santa muerte are very Catholic & have a huge space in their hearts, for both J.C. and Santisima Muerte. Bible-thumping crap, don't waste your time!
